If you have a question about this Privacy Policy, or you would like to contact us about any of your rights mentioned herein, please contact us at
support@planoly.com
. You may reach us by mail at Planogram, LLC, 1606 Headway Circle, Suite #9512, Austin, Texas 78754, USA.
